            <p>
              You are solely responsible for your conduct while using EMI3 and Applications within. You agree not to use EMI3 and Applications within for any unlawful or abusive purpose. You may not transmit or upload any material that is unlawful, defamatory, harassing, obscene, pornographic, or otherwise objectionable. You may not use EMI3 and Applications within to send spam, unsolicited emails, or other communications.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">3. User Accounts</h2>
            <p>
              In order to access EMI3 and applications within, you must create a user account. You agree to provide accurate and complete information when creating your user account. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account login information and for any activity that occurs under your account. You may not share your account login information with any third party.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p>
              EMI3 and applications within and all of its content, including but not limited to text, graphics, logos, images, and software, are the property of Equipment Management International P/L or its licensors and are protected by copyright, trademark, and other intellectual property laws. However, any content added or edited by clients, or their representatives shall remain the intellectual property of the respective client or representative.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p>
              Equipment Management International P/L and its officers, directors, employees, agents, and affiliates shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of EMI3 and applications within, including but not limited to damages for loss of profits, goodwill, use, data, or other intangible losses, even if Equipment Management International P/L has been advised of the possibility of such damages.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">6. Indemnification</h2>
            <p>
              You agree to indemnify and hold Equipment Management International P/L and its officers, directors, employees, agents, and affiliates harmless from any and all claims, damages, expenses, and liabilities, including attorneys' fees, arising from your use of EMI3 and applications within or your breach of these Terms of Use.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">7. Modifications</h2>
            <p>
              Equipment Management International P/L reserves the right to modify these Terms of Use at any time. Your continued use of EMI3 and applications within after such modifications shall constitute your acceptance of the modified Terms of Use.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
