          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">9. Governing Law</h2>
            <p>
              These Terms of Use shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of Tasmania, Australia, without giving effect to any principles of conflicts of law.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">10. Entire Agreement</h2>
